{"id":228620,"type":4,"name":"Florence","name_cn":"弗洛伦丝","date":"2018-02-13","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/54/96/228620_WPciC.jpg","rating":{"rank":5030,"total":317,"count":{"1":1,"2":1,"3":4,"4":7,"5":29,"6":82,"7":124,"8":57,"9":10,"10":2},"score":6.7},"summary":"《Florence》是一款讲述初恋的文字互动游戏，由澳大利亚的独立游戏工作室Mountains制作，创办者是前《纪念碑谷》的首席设计师Ken Wong。\r\n\r\nFlorence是一场持续约30分钟的心动体验。故事很简短，但意义很深远。\r\n\r\n25岁的Florence Yeoh对生活感到困惑。她的生活是日复一日地工作、睡觉，以及在社交媒体上打发大量时间。直到有一天，她遇到了一位名叫Krish的大提琴手，他改变了她眼中的整个世界。\r\n\r\n透过一系列预先设定的游戏剧本，从调情到吵架，从互助成长到逐渐分歧，玩家将体验Florence与Krish这段感情的点点滴滴。《Florence》的灵感来源于「Slice of Life」漫画小说和网络漫画，讲述了一个熟悉、青涩而又私密的爱情故事。\r\n\r\n内含原声音轨。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>弗洛伦丝</li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/33751\">Annapurna Interactive</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/10296\">Kevin Penkin</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>佛罗伦萨</li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Nintendo Switch</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Android</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>iOS</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>MacOS</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>AVG</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>Unity</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2018年2月13日(iOS)</li><li><span>售价: </span>¥ 26.00</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">售价: </span>$5.99</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://annapurna.pictures/interactive/florence</li><li><span>开发: </span>Mountains</li><li><span>游戏设计师: </span>Ken Wong、Kamina Vincent、Tony Coculuzzi、Sam Crisp</li><li><span>动画: </span>Jason Pamment</li><li><span>其他发行日期: </span>2020年2月13日(PC, NS)</li>","collection":{"on_hold":7,"dropped":1,"wish":70,"collect":430,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"独立游戏","count":66},{"name":"AVG","count":51},{"name":"手游","count":47},{"name":"文艺","count":41},{"name":"恋爱","count":34},{"name":"2018","count":24},{"name":"PC","count":22},{"name":"STEAM","count":20},{"name":"Android","count":19},{"name":"IOS","count":17},{"name":"PU